      "content": "hey, i need help with our e2e testing for the new web app. our CI/CD pipeline is a mess right now because of flaky tests causing builds to fail constantly, and the DevOps lead is breathing down my neck to get a stable branch for the release. \n\ncan u write a playwright test suite for the main user flow? (login -> dashboard -> profile update). it needs to be super robust so it doesn't trigger any false negatives in the pipeline. we really just need to make sure the build stays green for the deployment tomorrow. thanks.",
